'''α-鵝膏蕈鹼'''（'''α-amanitin'''）是一种八[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]的[[环肽|环肽]]，它可能是[[毒伞肽|毒伞肽]]中毒性最强的化合物。包括α-鵝膏蕈鹼的毒伞肽类物质主要存在于[[鵝膏菌屬|鵝膏菌屬]]的物种，例如[[毒鹅膏|毒鹅膏]]。α-鵝膏蕈鹼的口服半数致死量（{{LD50}}）约为0.1 mg/kg。

α-鵝膏蕈鹼的结构与一般多肽在氨基酸链的分支与连接上，除了8个残基组成的环外，其中的6-羟[[色氨酸|色氨酸]]和[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]桥连，形成了第二个“回路”。

与其它已知的真菌环肽不同，毒伞肽（还有毒肽类，例如[[鬼笔环肽|鬼笔环肽]]）的合成在[[核糖体|核糖体]]上。<ref>{{cite journal | author = H. Hallen, H. Luo, J.S. Scott-Craig, and J.D. Walton | year = 2007 | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences U.S.A. | volume = 104 | pages = 19097–19101 | url = http://www.pnas.org/content/104/48/19097 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0707340104 | title = A gene family encoding the major toxins of lethal Amanita mushrooms. | pmid = 18025465 | pmc = 2141914 | issue = 48 | access-date = 2013-12-09 | archive-date = 2022-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220107094147/https://www.pnas.org/content/104/48/19097 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
==毒理==
α-鵝膏蕈鹼是[[RNA聚合酶|RNA聚合酶]][[RNA聚合酶Ⅱ|II]]和[[RNA聚合酶Ⅲ|III]]的抑制剂，<ref>{{cite journal | author = B. Meinecke and S. Meinecke-Tillmann | year = 1993 | journal = Journal of Reproduction and Fertility | volume = 98 | pages = 195–201 | url = http://www.reproduction-online.org/cgi/content/abstract/98/1/195 | pmid = 8345464 | doi = 10.1530/jrf.0.0980195 | title = Effects of  -amanitin on nuclear maturation of porcine oocytes in vitro | issue = 1 | access-date = 2013-12-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928100115/http://www.reproduction-online.org/cgi/content/abstract/98/1/195 | archive-date = 2007-09-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>这种性质使其成为致命的毒素。
它被[[肝细胞|肝细胞]]摄入后，即与细胞中RNA聚合酶II和III强烈地结合，导致肝细胞溶解。<ref>{{cite journal | author = D. Michelot and R. Labia | year = 1988 | journal = Drug Metabol Drug Interact | volume = 6 | pages = 265–274 | pmid = 3078291 | title = alpha-Amanitin: a possible suicide substrate-like toxin involving the sulphoxide moiety of the bridged cyclopeptide. | issue = 3-4}}</ref>

==中毒症状==
摄入10小时内出现症状的报告极少，24小时内发生明显反应常见，发生明显反应时，有毒的食物早已通过胃，这种延迟易造成[[误诊|误诊]]，也使得中毒造成的危险性提高。[[腹泻|腹泻]]与[[抽搐|抽搐]]是早期症状，但这之后会经历一段虚假的缓解状态，直到第四至第五天，毒素开始对肝肾造成严重损伤，导致[[器官衰竭|器官功能衰竭]]，一般在一周左右[[死亡|死亡]]。<ref>{{cite journal | author = A. Mas | year = 2005 | title = Mushrooms | journal = Journal of Hepatology | volume = 42 | pages = 166–169 | url = http://www.jhep-elsevier.com/article/PIIS0168827804006002/fulltext | doi = 10.1016/j.jhep.2004.12.003 | pmid = 15664239 | issue = 2 }}</ref>

大约15%的α-鵝膏蕈鹼中毒者在10天内死亡，通常是陷入[[昏迷|昏迷]]，然后进展到[[肾功能衰竭|肾功能衰竭]]、[[肝功能衰竭|肝功能衰竭]]、[[肝昏迷|肝昏迷]]、[[呼吸衰竭|呼吸衰竭]]直至死亡。即使痊愈也留有永久性肝损伤的风险。<ref name ="benjamin95">{{cite journal |author=Benjamin DR |title=Amatoxin syndrome |pages=198–214}} in: {{cite book |title=Mushrooms: poisons and panaceas — a handbook for naturalists, mycologists and physicians |url=https://archive.org/details/mushroomspoisons0000benj |publisher=New York: WH Freeman and Company |year=1995}}</ref>
